-- Unilever Ghana Expects to Double Profit in Second Half of Year, CEO Says
-- Moses Dzawu
-- 2010-07-27T14:02:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/unilever-ghana-expects-to-double-profit-in-second-half-of-year-ceo-says.html

          
          
             Unilever Ghana Ltd. expects to
double its first-half profit in the remaining six months of the
year, Chief Executive Officer Charles Cofie said in an interview
in the capital, Accra, today.  
